---
description: Rules for interacting with the AI OS Notion workspace
alwaysApply: false
---

- When asked to sync Notion, search for existing records before creating new ones.
- Treat Notion as the operational system of record.
- Keep updates minimal and structured.
- Prefer creating or updating these records during kickoff:
  - Project: Konative.com
  - Site Registry: konative.com
  - Milestones for kickoff
  - Planned Block Library entries
- Log all Notion actions in the response.
- If database structure differs from expectation, inspect first and adapt carefully.
